{"tid":353820,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"狗都唔屌既煙腸真係連射波既資格都冇","createTime":"2017-08-10T02:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T17:04:34.000Z","uid":108685,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4dc9c1ee6617f1c62725f72bbad8ba2cca3c82c","tid":353820,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:40:29.000Z","msg":"煙腸人工有幾多唔使講啦<br />\n好聽d就叫津貼 如果唔係最低工資都唔過 俾人告都似<br />\nok 人工低咪使少d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日返九粒 長短週 <br />\n即係一個星期可能得一日有自然醒既機會<br />\n同事又年紀較大又唔會點講野 <br />\n開頭未做過office 覺得做既野都覺得幾新鮮<br />\n再做落下都係做果d文書工作 聽下電話咁<br />\n覺得增加唔到對工作行業既認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返到頹晒 想射日波都難<br />\n老師又唔想你請事假 又要經佢批又要經上司批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請病假要醫生紙都好正常啫 <br />\n問題係請假會連果一百幾蚊一日既糧都冇埋<br />\n然後再倒貼百幾蚊睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又唔鍾意係醫生面前詐病 覺得醫生實知好老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通想休息日都咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 長工當然辛苦啦 但係煙腸真係頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預左俾人插唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20e0d21db5223187d9a904cfe79ea1c4b4981cd","tid":353820,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d804879a39439a5f0ae9302f53c35648d82515","tid":353820,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgm